& verify if the first value is 0 and the second is more than 0.
1 ZER A 2 4
    2 ZER B 100 3
        3  ADD C 100

& if B is zero and A not is, A > B
4 ZER B 100 5

& iterative subtraction in the A and B
5 ZER A 100 6
    6 SUB A 7
    7 SUB B 8
    8 ZER A 9 5
        9 ZER B 100 10
        10 ADD C 100

